commit.message:
Improve the candidates to cursor behavior.

1. filter candidate by align to the next segment.
   e.g.  a|ng -> will filter at ang.
         xi|an -> filter till xi.
2. Add a new sentence from lattice. This is ideally the sentence till
   cursor. To avoid extra computation, we don't compute nbest here.

commit.message:
Handle customized single char final mapping

When a single char final (aeiouv) is remapped in profile, we should
consider applying the rule based on the character that it maps to, and
not apply it to the original character.

To do this, we just simply remove all stringToFinal(c) logic, and solely
relies on the finalMap_ to do the trick. finalMap_ will be filled with
extra omitted single char final entries so all the rest logic can be
unified.

Fix #62

The model score we actually miss part so the model item has wrong high
score.

We should compare P(..|A) * P(..A|B) with P(..|ACD), not compare
P(...|ACD) with P(..A|B).
